name: RED (from PRIDE)
description:
Red is the fire protagonist from my older project PRIDE.
PRIDE was a fighting game relating to a world where everybody has superpowers.

Red has been fused with Chaos power.
PRIDE was renamed to POWERDRIVE at a later stage of development then halted because of the graphics loading library which prevented the game from working on anything else than Windows PC.
My new project is the Galaxy Game (PC/Mobile/Consoles)
